{"id": 1312, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X三星盖乐世On】为了脱离单身狗的行列，你都潜心修炼过哪些技能？", "description": "嗯，为爱千锤百炼，提早成了女友奴。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5255, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161104210906BIHjVh3ctvJr4laT.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-09T03:00:55Z", "options": [{"id": 132096, "content": "炼就了一身私家（视）侦探（奸）技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627887}, {"id": 132097, "content": "下了blued （捂脸逃）", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753619}, {"id": 132098, "content": "虽然只打打电话上上网，但还是装逼买好手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 132099, "content": "特别想做好几件事、结果把自己逼疯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792030}, {"id": 133891, "content": "强行插入广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833292}, {"id": 132100, "content": "买个宝马方便装逼用", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 132101, "content": "哈喽", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515906}, {"id": 132102, "content": "技♂术", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815634}, {"id": 132360, "content": "总觉得…今天的广告特别多～ 看了3个了已经", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232979}, {"id": 132106, "content": "看他看的书，听他听的歌，走他走过的路和看过的风景。然后练就一个无比独立能吃能睡的自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 132107, "content": "单机 局域网  大型网游。lol wow 阴阳师  cs，来什么会什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773277}, {"id": 132114, "content": "不买note7。", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 132116, "content": "听古典音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 132117, "content": "三星再见= =", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789122}, {"id": 132118, "content": "坚持听莫扎特贝多芬柴可夫斯基……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500910}, {"id": 132119, "content": "把宫崎骏的作品潜心研究，只因她现在在追", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825368}, {"id": 132120, "content": "送女朋友手机千万不能送三星", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41188}, {"id": 133144, "content": "化妆，装不喜欢，表白", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831014}, {"id": 132121, "content": "如果练过了我还会是单身狗嘛。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440054}, {"id": 132122, "content": "单身了两年想变成更好的自己，最后真的就单身下去了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826782}, {"id": 132123, "content": "尝试突破自己，像心仪男生搭讪罗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792677}, {"id": 130587, "content": "买个拍夜景都能把人拍美的手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 134428, "content": "不在伤心   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802079}, {"id": 130588, "content": "手机开好一指秒付，以便随时给我对象买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 132125, "content": "三丧再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467223}, {"id": 130589, "content": "买大容量手机，不在关键时刻掉链子", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 132126, "content": "修的一手好厨艺", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600837}, {"id": 132127, "content": "健身", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717259}, {"id": 132136, "content": "卸了blued", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699020}, {"id": 132137, "content": "刷完了知乎所有关于套路的回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565950}, {"id": 135465, "content": "强迫自己打自认为很无聊的游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840189}, {"id": 132138, "content": "申请信用卡，刷卡免密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}, {"id": 132139, "content": "啦啦啦啦啦阿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826833}, {"id": 132140, "content": "男友白衬衫买起来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826083}, {"id": 132141, "content": "强行掰弯了自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 132142, "content": "为了拍好照片学摄影，为了知识广点，坚持看书，为了体型好点，坚持健身，为了增加自己阅历，坚持走不同的地方和不同的人聊天，后来习惯了一个人享受孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254661}, {"id": 132143, "content": "练就一手好厨艺，和满身逗逼气质", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816771}, {"id": 132144, "content": "学会美美哒\nand始终勇敢\n——٩(๑❛ᴗ❛๑)۶男票自来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777224}, {"id": 132146, "content": "不顾一切，凭着一口气坚持把自己打造的更完美。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 815558}, {"id": 132147, "content": "买S8 E", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307529}, {"id": 132148, "content": "学习对抗套路的反套路技能?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826372}, {"id": 132149, "content": "请不要和三星合作", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826923}, {"id": 132150, "content": "好奇心不是没有“小编”嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117629}, {"id": 135990, "content": "期待note8", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842375}, {"id": 132153, "content": "变帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144586}, {"id": 132154, "content": "还没对象的被塞了一嘴狗粮", 